Server Economics:<BR>
The concept is not that the item would be sold, but rather once an item is so common, it begins to loose it's value (price or esteem).<BR>
He referenced items that used to go for quite a bit of money, but are now given to twinks since they have become worthless to sell.<BR>
Remember when all melees hoped to have a Yak?  Now lvl 12's are running around with them 'cause there are so many.<BR>
Once every cleric has an epic, they will want something better than an epic.<BR>
If enough people have them and rezing becomes too easy, death stops becoming the penalty that Verant wants it to be.<BR>
<BR>
